Name: Moon  Defense
About the game: Moon Defense - protection of a lunar settlement from falling meteorites. You have to go through 8 levels to defend the lunar settlement. Each level is distinguished by a timer for protection, the number and durability of meteorites falling on you. By earning credits for defending a settlement, you can upgrade your rocket launcher and the defense of the settlement.
